azureLogAnalytics.query:
union AppDependencies,
AppRequests,
AppExceptions,
AppTraces
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| summarize by RoleName
| summarize Count=count()

AppRequests
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=count() by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success != 1
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=count() by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=count() by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success != 1
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=count() by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppDependencies
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success != 1
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=dcount(Target) by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppExceptions
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Count=count() by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

union withsource=SourceTable
AppAvailabilityResults,
AppBrowserTimings,
AppDependencies,
AppEvents,
AppExceptions,
AppMetrics,
AppPageViews,
AppPerformanceCounters,
AppRequests,
AppSystemEvents,
AppTraces
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| summarize Volume=sum(_BilledSize) by TimeGenerated=bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval)
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppDependencies
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| extend DependencyType = case(DependencyType contains "http", "HTTP", DependencyType)
| where Success == false
| summarize Failed=sum(ItemCount) by DependencyType, Target
| top 5 by Failed

AppExceptions
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| extend Type = tostring(split(ExceptionType, ".")[-1])
| extend Exception = strcat(Type, ' | ', tostring(split(RoleName, "|")[0]))
| summarize Failed=count() by Exception
| top 5 by Failed
| order by Failed desc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success == false
| where ResultCode != "404"
| extend Request = strcat(AppRoleName, " | ", Name)
| summarize Failed=sum(ItemCount) by Request
| top 5 by Failed

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Name != "GET /healthcheck" and Name != "HEAD /healthcheck"
| where Success == true
| extend Request = strcat(AppRoleName, " | ", Name)
| summarize Failed=sum(ItemCount) by Request
| top 5 by Failed

AppRequests
| where OperationName !contains "health"
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| where ResultCode !startswith "404"
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| summarize percent=avg(Success), Requests=count() by RoleName 
| where Requests > 100
| project-away Requests
| extend percent = (1 - percent) * 100
| where percent != 0
| order by percent desc
| top 10 by percent

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| summarize Total=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| summarize requests=avg(DurationMs) by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success == 0
| summarize requests=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName, ResultCode 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success == 0 and ResultCode startswith "4"
| summarize requests=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName, ResultCode 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success == 0 and ResultCode !startswith "4" and ResultCode !startswith "5"
| summarize requests=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName, ResultCode 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

AppRequests
| where $__timeFilter(TimeGenerated)
| extend RoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName == "1", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| where $__contains(RoleName, $Apps)
| where Success == 0 and ResultCode startswith "5"
| summarize requests=count() by bin(TimeGenerated, $__interval), RoleName, ResultCode 
| order by TimeGenerated asc

list.definition:
union
workspace("$Workspace").AppDependencies,
workspace("$Workspace").AppRequests,
workspace("$Workspace").AppExceptions,
workspace("$Workspace").AppTraces,
workspace("$Workspace").AppPerformanceCounters,
workspace("$Workspace").AppEvents
| summarize by AppRoleName
| extend AppRoleName = case(AppRoleName == "", "Unknown", AppRoleName)
| order by AppRoleName asc
